PrecisAmendment to the QUEEN'S REGULATIONS AND ORDERS FOR THE CANADIAN FORCES prescribing that the Chief Military Trial Judge is the officer who must appoint the President and members of a General Court Martial and a Disciplinary Court Martial and providing the reasons for not appointing an officer selected by random methodology to perform court martial duties as a President or member.
